- Uh-oh.</i>

00:59.459 --> 01:03.020
Because it's time for
Bill and Marty's 5:00 news ''flush.''

01:03.129 --> 01:06.292
<i>- [ Toilet Flushing ]
- ##[ Man Singing ]</i>

01:06.399 --> 01:08.390
- Our topless story-
- [ Boing ]

01:08.501 --> 01:11.197
President Clinton
has launched a new Web site.

01:11.304 --> 01:14.637
- Uh-oh. Wait. Let me guess. WWW dot-
- [ Wolf Whistle ]

01:14.741 --> 01:15.799
- dot-
- [ Boing ]

